timeline.bodyText:
Reason the PR build fails is that these README code samples are generated based on the line range listed in the embedme comment.
You'll want to add the new lines of code into that section and update the line range references. Then run the following to regenerate the README with the changes you made.
mvn package -DskipTests -Dreadme-codesnippet{-windows} -f {target POM}
It will modify the README associated to the target POM, you'll want to verify it looks correct. Then to ensure that CI will pass you'll want to run the following, which is the same as CI will do.
mvn package -DskipTests -Dverify-readme{-windows} -f {target POM}
For the commands above add {-windows} if you're using a Windows machine, otherwise omit it.
